>>>>>>>>>>>> VM's
>>>>>>>>>>>> dma-resv lock.
>>>>>>>>>>> Yes, that made me a bit curious because in the current 
>>>>>>>>>>> version the code
>>>>>>>>>>> required the object's dma_resv for unlink() which can't be 
>>>>>>>>>>> grabbed
>>>>>>>>>>> either from the fence signaling path. So are there any 
